                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9252" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2316</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">965 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">幸福民企管理密码：黑松林公司的心力管理之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Management Code of a Happy Private Enterprise: The Way of Mental Power Management at Heisonglin Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吴海宁，郭春祎，潘多英，吴晶晶</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏黑松林粘合剂厂有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">幸福民企；心力管理；党建工作；爱国敬业；回报社会；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Happy Private Enterprise, Mental Power Management, Party Building Work, Patriotic Dedication, Return To The Society</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑松林公司董事长刘鹏凯在30多年企业管理经验中找到了建设幸福企业的管理密码。在日复一日的管理实践中，董事长刘鹏凯与员工、客户、大学教授交流互动，形成了独具特色的心力管理的完整体系。在企业高质量发展的背景下，刘鹏凯在加强民营企业党建工作、培养员工爱国敬业、回报社会发展的发展升华了心力管理的思想，使其成为在民营企业向“专精特新”发展，实现员工与企业，企业与社会和谐发展的典型企业。本案例帮助学生理解心力管理的内涵和发展历程，特别是心力管理在适应党和国家发展要求背景下的升华过程，探讨刘鹏凯如何在适应复杂环境的过程中，不断深化企业家的管理思想，建设幸福企业的过程。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Over more than 30 years of corporate management experience, Liu Pengkai, the chairman of Heisonglin Company, has discovered the management code for building a happy enterprise. Through daily management practices and interactions with employees, customers, and university professors, Liu Pengkai has formed a unique and comprehensive system of mental power management. Against the backdrop of high-quality corporate development, Liu Pengkai has further enriched the idea of mental power management by strengthening the Party building work in private enterprises, fostering patriotism and professional dedication among employees, and contributing to societal progress. This has made Heisonglin a model enterprise that pursues specialized, refined, innovative, and cutting-edge development, achieving harmonious coexistence between employees, the enterprise, and society. This case study aims to help students understand the essence and development process of mental power management, especially its refinement in adapting to the development requirements of the Party and the country. It also explores how Liu Pengkai has continuously deepened his entrepreneurial management thinking and constructed a happy enterprise in a complex environment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">愿景的内涵；通过对詹姆士&#183;马奇对管理者认知分析框架的学习，讨论刘鹏凯在不同阶段关注的焦点有何不同；通过对要素匹配理论的理解和应用分析要素的关系，讨论黑松林心力管理如何支持企业成为幸福企业；讨论刘鹏凯建设幸福企业的做法对其他中小民营企业管理者的启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
